headline: Mastercard Names Accenture Veteran as New CMO
summary: Jill Kramer will succeed Raja Rajamannar, who led marketing and communications at the payments company for almost 13 years.

headline: Accenture and AWS Accelerate AI-Powered Reinvention and Cloud Modernization for Public Service Organizations
summary: NEW YORK, October 21, 2025--Accenture announced an expansion of its collaboration with Amazon Web Services (AWS) to deliver transformative digital services to public sector.
